 vp\u0159ed o {seekOffset} s","Network Error":"Chyba s\xEDt\u011B","Decode Error":"Chyba dek\xF3dov\xE1n\xED","Source Not Supported":"Zdroj nen\xED podporov\xE1n","Encryption Error":"Chyba \u0161ifrov\xE1n\xED","A network error caused the media download to fail.":"Chyba s\xEDt\u011B zp\u016Fsobila selh\xE1n\xED stahov\xE1n\xED m\xE9di\xED.","A media error caused playback to be aborted. The media could be corrupt or your browser does not support this format.":"Chyba m\xE9di\xED zp\u016Fsobila p\u0159eru\u0161en\xED p\u0159ehr\xE1v\xE1n\xED. M\xE9dia mohou b\xFDt po\u0161kozena nebo v\xE1\u0161 prohl\xED\u017Ee\u010D nepodporuje tento form\xE1t.","An unsupported error occurred. The server or network failed, or your browser does not support this format.":"Do\u0161lo k nepodporovan\xE9 chyb\u011B. Server nebo s\xED\u0165 selhaly, nebo v\xE1\u0161 prohl\xED\u017Ee\u010D nepodporuje tento form\xE1t.","The media is encrypted and there are no keys to decrypt it.":"M\xE9dia jsou \u0161ifrov\xE1na a neexistuj\xED \u017E\xE1dn\xE9 kl\xED\u010De k jejich de\u0161ifrov\xE1n\xED."};var Rp={"Start airplay":"Start AirPlay","Stop airplay":"Stop AirPlay",Audio:"Lyd",Captions:"Undertekster","Enable captions":"Sl\xE5 undertekster til","Disable captions":"Sl\xE5 undertekster fra","Start casting":"Start casting","Stop casting":"Stop casting","Enter fullscreen mode":"Sl\xE5 fuldsk\xE6rm til","Exit fullscreen mode":"Sl\xE5 fuldsk\xE6rm fra",Mute:"Sl\xE5 lyden fra",Unmute:"Sl\xE5 lyden til","Enter picture in picture mode":"Aktiv\xE9r billede-i-billede-tilstand","Exit picture in picture mode":"Afslut billede-i-billede-tilstand",Play:"Afspil",Pause:"Pause","Playback rate":"Afspilningshastighed","Playback rate {playbackRate}":"Afspilningshastighed {playbackRate}",Quality:"Kvalitet","Seek backward":"Spol tilbage","Seek forward":"Spol frem",Settings:"Indstillinger",Auto:"Auto","audio player":"lydafspiller","video player":"videoafspiller",volume:"Lydstyrke",seek:"S\xF8g","closed captions":"Undert